  "texts": [
    "Because the algorithm for finding MIS is random, we ran it 20,000 times and selected the largest MIS across the runs.",
    "For the brain, the MIS consisted of 159 barcodes, 121 of which were randomly assigned to the genes.",
    "For the kidney, the MIS had 269 barcodes.",
    "We randomly added 31 additional barcodes and counted the number of edges of the induced subgraph of G with the selected nodes.",
    "We repeated this selection 20,000 times and proceeded with the run with the lowest edge count."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}